                    <span class="heading">How is Fake News spread</span>
                    
                    <span class="content">Fake news is spread through social media to reach receptive audiences.</span>

                    <span class="content">Twitter and Facebook are the most prominent platforms for social media manipulation.The use of ‘bots’ amplify manipulated contents.</span>

                    <span class="content">Cookies are used to track people's visit to websites and thus create personality profiles, and show people fake news content that they are most receptive to.</span>
                </div>
            </div>
