                    <span class="content">Embed media literacy into school curriculum.</span>

                    <span class="content">Read the entire piece before you decide whether or not to share.</span>

                    <span class="content">Don't stay in your own echo chamber.</span>

                    <span class="content">Use Factcheck tools such as Factcheck.org</span>
